com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message

Class DistributedCollectionMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message.DistributedCollectionMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalizableData, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NopMessage, ReplayRequestMessage, ReplayResponseMessage, WriteRequestMessage

    public abstract class DistributedCollectionMessage
extends Object
implements ExternalizableData, Cloneable
    Base class for all distributed collection messages.

    Subclasses are expected to implement their own specific dispatching behaviour.

    See Also:
    IDistributedCollectionMessageListener, dispatch(IDistributedCollectionMessageListener)
